Equinox EQ-BP 36 Upper Arm Bp Monitor (White and Blue) Price: Rs.3550

Key Features

  • Ascultory Measurement
Blood pressure measured at a doctor's clinic might give you an elevated pressure due to fear and nervousness known as white-coat hypertension; hence Equinox EQ-BP 36 BP monitor could be resourceful in tackling this problem. This Equinox BP monitor provides automatic blood pressure measurement and gives you the flexibility of measuring your BP at your home.

Equipped with an automatic power-off function the BP monitor automatically shuts down if the monitor is idle for more than 3 minutes. The Equinox EQ-BP 36 arm BP monitor also incorporates Arterial stiffness index which generates information on the stiffness and flexibility of your brachial artery thus indicating you of possible vascular diseases such as arteriosclerosis.

Build

The upper arm blood pressure monitor by Equinox is small and compact with a user-friendly interface. The BP monitor is composed of the main unit and a non-integrated cuff. The main unit comprises of a large and clear LCD display and control buttons. The cuff can be easily attached to arm sizes ranging from a circumference of 24 to 34 cm. The monitor is easy to operate all you need to do is attach the cuff to your arms and press the control button for smooth functioning of the BP monitor.

Performance and Features

The Equinox blood pressure monitor uses the Oscillometric method to determine your blood pressure. This automatic BP monitor uses the Ausculatory method of measurement as a reference for its clinical trial in order to meet accuracy standards. The Ausculatory method detects audible sounds on your arterial wall. Based on the presence and disappearance of these audible sounds your systolic/diastolic readings are taken.

The electro-pneumatic pump integrated in this arm BP monitor enables the cuff to inflate automatically giving you quick digitized readings that are accurate. This Equinox BP monitor also incorporates a memory function that stores 3 x 12 measurements with average. The BP monitor measures your 3 readings first and then saves the average of these readings. The arm BP monitor is capable of storing 12 such average readings.

Capable of displaying a wide range of pressure and pulse readings the EQ-BP 36 Equinox BP monitor displays readings ranging from 20 mmHg to 280 mmHg for pressure and 40 to 199 beats/minute for pulse rates. The accuracy rate of the monitor stands at +/-3 mmHg for pressure and +/-5% of reading for pulse progress. This Equinox arm BP monitor operates on 4 AA batteries.

Key Features

  • 5 micro m Particle Size
  • 7 ml Medication Capacity
  • Non-heating Compressor
  • 1900 g Weight
  • Average Nebulization Rate at 0.4 ml / min
Equinox EQ-NL 72 Nebulizer is ideal for those undergoing medical treatment related to asthma cystic fibrosis or any other ailments in the respiratory system. This compressor nebulizer is employed to transform liquid medication solution into fine aerosol or mist-like particles that can be properly inhaled by you through a mouthpiece or a face mask.

Unlike many conventional compressor nebulizers that generate undesired heating of the compressor this Equinox nebulizer is powered with a non-heating compressor unit which prevents the unrequired heating.

Body

Small and compact the Equinox compressor nebulizer weighs about 1900 g. and can come handy while you are travelling. The nebulizer is crafted to bring about simple and easy operation. The device comes in four main parts comprising of the compressor unit air tube medication or nebulization cup and a mouthpiece or face mask.

The compressor unit is compact and houses an on/off switch to control the device. The air tube connects the unit to the medication cup and the mouthpiece. The medication cup can hold 7 ml of your prescribed medicine. You have the option of using the mouthpiece or the face mask to administer this prescribed medication. The nebulizer machine comes with face masks for both adult and children hence making the device ideal for all ages.

Performance and Features

This EQ-NL 72 compressor nebulizer by Equinox can deliver high concentration of aerosol to your lungs as the device operates at an average nebulization rate of 0.4 ml per min. The nebulizer machine supplies oxygen to the medication solution converting it into particle sizes that vary from 0.5 to 5 µm.

The Equinox EQ-NL 72 nebulizer provides 5 replaceable filters which can reduce the chance of infection by removing bacteria from the oxygen delivered to you. These particles are then delivered to the lower airways in your lungs to provide an effective treatment for your respiratory problems.

In order to operate soundly the nebulizer machine requires a temperature ranging from 10 to 40 degree Celsius and humidity ranging from 30 to 85% RH. Storing the Equinox EQ-NL 72 nebulizer machine would be ideal at a temperature range of -20 to 60 degree Celsius with humidity range of 10 to 95% RH. The compressor nebulizer device is powered by 230 V 50/60 Hz of electricity and consumes 138 W of the power supply.

Equinox EQ-BP 54 Upper Arm Bp Monitor (White and Blue) Price: Rs.1200

Key Features

  • Ascultory Measurement
With the Equinox EQ-BP 54 Upper Arm BP monitor assessing your blood pressure becomes easy as the monitor provides an automatic measurement revealing consistent and accurate readings. The BP monitor is also integrated with an automatic power-off that enhances your battery-life as the device shuts down when it is idle for more than 3 minutes.

Build

The Equinox upper arm BP monitor is built for ease of use as the device is portable and handy. The BP monitor comes with two main parts; the main control unit and the separate cuff attachment. The main unit houses a large LCD display for easy viewing and simple control buttons. The arm blood pressure monitor provides you with a standard sized cuff that fits into various arm sizes ranging from 24 to 34 cm in diameter.

Performance and Features

This EQ-BP 54 BP monitor by Equinox employs the Oscillometric method to determine your blood pressure. Using the Ausculatory method as a reference for its clinical trial the BP monitor is accurate and efficient. The Ausculatory method of measurement senses the audible sounds of your blood flow on the arterial wall. Thereafter which your systolic and diastolic readings are measured based on the presence and disappearance of these audible sounds.

Vested with an in-built electro-pneumatic pump this Equinox BP monitor automatically inflates the cuff thereby leading to an automatic measurement operation. This Equinox arm BP monitor also features a memory of 3 x 12 measurements with average. The arm BP monitor first measures your 3 readings and stores the average of these readings after which the monitor saves 12 such average readings. This could be useful for recording and recalling your blood pressure history.

This Equinox automatic upper arm blood pressure monitor displays readings ranging from 20 mmHg to 280 mmHg for pressure and 40 to 199 beats/minute for pulse rates. A simultaneous display of both systolic/diastolic pressure readings and pulse rates are digitally shown on the LCD display. Accurate and efficient this BP monitor is regulated at +/-3 mmHg for pressure and +/-5% of reading for pulse progress. The upper arm blood pressure monitor uses 4 AA batteries to function soundly.

Key Features

  • Step On Analyser
  • 1 Operation Mode
  • 150 kg Max Weight Capacity
  • 10 Memory Preset
  • Auto Shut Off
  • Battery Powered

You may appear slim in the mirror but excess body fat can still make you susceptible to heart disorders diabetes high blood pressure and other illnesses. With Equinox EQ 33 Body Fat Analyzer you can regularly monitor your fat levels and determine whether you are at high risk or not. This EB-EQ33 from Equinox Home Health care provides an innovative solution to improve your health and well-being.

This health care product is a Step-On Ananlyzer; you should step on it with bare feet as this equipment has galvanized electrodes that send a small painless current of electric signal up through your legs to the entire body and back down. This Equinox health care device is portable so you can comfortably carry it everywhere you go. The Equinox EQ 33 Body Fat Analyzer comes with a Graduation of 100 gm.

Body and Power

The EB-EQ33 features an elegant Metallic-Optic design that renders the device a sleek look. After the information input the results appear on a Digital Display; the size of the LCD digits measures 1.5 inches which is very convenient to read. This Equinox health care equipment uses a unique measurement technique called Bioelectrical Impedance Analysis these scales send a small harmless electrical current through your body when you step on the scale. This current passes more slowly through fat than muscle giving you a measurement of how much fat is in your body compared to the muscle or your body fat percentage.

This health care device utilizes a cutting edge technology the Strain Gauge Sensor a conducting material fitted in the device used to measure strain. This device under stress is sensitive to any small change and the sensors convert it into usable signals which are displayed on the LCD. This Equinox EQ 33 Body Fat Analyzer is used to determine 0-80 per cent of body fat 10-80 per cent of body water 13-100 per cent of muscle and 0-9 per cent bone.

The results of this Body Fat Analyzer are accurate and you can effectively use the information to track your weight loss goals and success. To obtain best results you should always weigh yourself at the same time under same conditions. This Equinox Body Fat Analyzer requires 4 x 1.5 V of power to work efficiently.

Performance

The health care device comes with a personal profile set-up and memory chip can store data for up to 10 persons.  The LCD digital display of this Equinox health care equipment features Auto zero and Auto off; this feature enables you to take readings conveniently as you don’t have to reset the LCD display every time you use it. The Equinox EQ 33 Body Fat Analyzer has quick 0.1 per cent interval display of body fat water and muscle mass.  The easy to use light weight and portable Equinox Body Fat Analyzer shows you immediately whether your diet or exercise program is effectively reducing your body fat.
